Package edu.cnm.deepdive.abq_film_tour_backend.controller

Class FilmLocationController

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cnm.deepdive.abq_film_tour_backend.controller.FilmLocationController
  • @RestController
@ExposesResourceFor(FilmLocation.class)
@RequestMapping("/film_locations")
public class FilmLocationController
extends Object
    The controller for the FilmLocation entity, which also includes functionality for userComments and Images associated with the entity. Requires an associated GoogleUser.
